{"tid":1798870,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜火辣激露屁股蛋 「韓國最強肉體」摸乳互尬","createTime":"2019-12-26T14:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T21:45:51.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5a7fcf2fd51e4b8486945f66536dcd293256b5","tid":1798870,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/12/25/phpJZQnxZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F12%2F25%2FphpJZQnxZ.jpg&h=8c83b9fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜（右）與雪炫（左）火辣互尬。（翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7G4eyi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7G4eyi.png&h=f33d9d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔記者曾德蓉／台北報導〕韓國女團「TWICE」成員周子瑜，昨在SBS歌謠大戰帶來特別舞台《Do You？》，與有「韓國最強肉體」封號的「AOA」成員雪炫熱舞，雙姝火辣互尬，馬上引起全場暴動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/12/25/phpJNSPGR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F12%2F25%2FphpJNSPGR.jpg&h=8fa67081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜（圖）與雪炫火辣互尬。（翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n子瑜昨晚展現性感風情，薄紗火辣露出腿根，與雪炫在SBS歌謠大戰上帶來特別舞台《Do You？》，身為前輩的雪炫，舉手投足充滿女王氣場，還出現摸乳動作，子瑜也不遑多讓，每個舞步都挑逗觀眾，一個彎腰，屁股蛋也在走光邊緣，雙姝互尬令網友忍不住激讚「神仙打架」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/12/25/php39Vddr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F12%2F25%2Fphp39Vddr.jpg&h=b0503ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜與雪炫（圖）火辣互尬。（翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjZJu6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjZJu6G.jpg&h=fa8784d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相關影音：（影片取自YouTube，如遭移除敬請見諒）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AUm4eyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAUm4eyp.jpg&h=747d586f&s={SIZE}\" />